B.avM=new A.I("EMG/NCS is the gold standard for confirming radiculopathy because it provides objective evidence of nerve root dysfunction that imaging alone cannot. Up to 30% of asymptomatic adults have disc herniations on MRI that cause zero symptoms. The EMG tells you whether the nerve root is actually injured, how severely, and whether it is acute or chronic.",null,B.j_,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
