B.II=new A.fc("Pattern","Is it perfectly regular (CRDs), irregular (fibrillations), or bursting (myokymia)?")
B.IE=new A.fc("Rhythm","Distinguish between a semi-rhythmic 'rain on a tin roof' vs. perfectly regular 'machine-like' firing.")
B.IC=new A.fc("Recruitment","Observe how units activate with increasing force. Does the rate go up, or do more units jump in?")
B.Iy=new A.fc("Voluntary Control","Remember this pearl: Nobody has voluntary control under 4-5Hz. If it's firing at 2Hz, it's spontaneous.")
